pg&h=70e68fb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都驚有木蚤，所以裝好左之後我會用煙霧蛋同滴露全部傢私再抹一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望無事"},{"pid":"494f2227e16b942fe6b5544be0eefcff2cfea867","tid":7793,"uid":23869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T10:56:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>岩岩訂左未送到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打買左邊款</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/28/173438_385d481224c3f43f01e5ad7f09231cd7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F28%2F173438_385d481224c3f43f01e5ad7f09231cd7.jpg&h=02c8a9d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都驚有木蚤，所以裝好左之後我會用煙霧蛋同滴露全部傢私再抹一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望無事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一兩塊板 冇事嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0299e789b47c351ef32e462e476bc0453b7824d6","tid":7793,"uid":45983,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T13:43:06.000Z","msg":"買過3塊，用左兩年都無事"},{"pid":"d574c5c0e3593abb122c7e19d91fc6dc0141a658","tid":7793,"uid":45769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T04:12:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/01/121200_0a8ea19720b3b14bf9afb333b466d1e6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F01%2F121200_0a8ea19720b3b14bf9afb333b466d1e6.jpg&h=f8efa10b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搭單一問<br />\n小弟想淘張呢啲<br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲淘過？<br />\n<br />\n同埋黎緊雙12<br />\n有無咩正傢私推薦下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33c7ab908899ff0d7dae0fcb7a174f86bf12b16e","tid":7793,"uid":45769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T04:34:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>因小失大，成間屋有木蝨既話，你可以拎定10萬8萬出黎都得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多鳩餘<br />\n香港買咪又係大陸造</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港買如果搞到你成屋木蝨都仲有得嘈 支那寶買落黎有時你搵邊個</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正常住家裝修D櫃咪又係支那造</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全屋傢私 我都上大陸訂造啦  身邊朋友 都係 都無咩問題<br />\n老實講<br />\n香港啲裝修判頭<br />\n有八成都係大陸訂造落黎<br />\n<br />\n裝修完無幾耐生蟲 咁無撚計  個人黑系起上黎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n過耐左先講生蟲果啲<br />\n其實好多時係屋企好撚潮濕  又污糟而引發 <br />\n<br />\n又或者本身有養動物 野返黎  唔奇怪<br />\n<br />\n都係果句  勤清潔 好啲"},{"pid":"354b89ea8130718da3b5e30abda3e48e9545c41c","tid":7793,"uid":23869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:22:21.000Z","msg":"決定雙十二買板<br />\n運到黎用藍威寶抺下算"}]}